{"tid":599419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"單車男氣槍射途人","createTime":"2018-03-20T11:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T13:23:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b69a55eb8cdcd32736532911a0b5d04cedd00308","tid":599419,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180320/20337156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F20337156&d=AViq3vxGpG8D50IWgIFLqFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=2933fc79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F20337156&h=f679460d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180320/20337156</a><br />\n<br />\n單車男氣槍射途人<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n女事主遭氣槍射傷右耳後到醫院敷治。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名51歲女子昨下午在元朗水邊圍邨街頭，遭一名騎單車的尼泊爾裔少年用氣槍射傷右耳，兇徒事後騎單車逃去，警方正展開追緝。<br />\n<br />\n女事主右耳受傷<br />\n<br />\n女事主姓鄭，家住水邊圍邨康水樓，昨日下午4時許，她在家進食後落樓打算買汽水，當她行至媽廟路準備過馬路時，突然聽聞3響「噗噗」聲，並在最後一聲響後，感覺右耳刺痛，轉身一看，赫見一名騎着單車的10餘歲疑是尼泊爾裔少年手持一支短氣槍望着她。<br />\n<br />\n鄭懷疑對方用氣槍射她，立即上前質問對方：「有冇搞錯，亂咁開槍，射到人呀！」但少年沒有理睬，隨即騎着單車逃去。<br />\n女事主追趕不及於是報警，警員及救護員接報到場將事主送往醫院敷治。警員在事發現場附近兜截無果。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姜偉康"},{"pid":"940292562304369ab4db6c47b9e39a157392dbd2","tid":599419,"uid":4739,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"土耳其火槍兵"},{"pid":"5df7d2e198fdf8746e3da08ea20898108db7e1c3","tid":599419,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"940292562304369ab4db6c47b9e39a157392dbd2","tid":599419,"uid":4739,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"土耳其火槍兵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/